2647,IssuesEvent,2017-09-03 03:59:05+00:00,2909429,nicolargo/glances,28420625,altek86,,,opened,Can you add qnap support?,[],[],0,"Before filling this issue, please read the manual (https://glances.readthedocs.io/en/latest/) and search if the bug do not already exists in the database (https://github.com/nicolargo/glances/issues).

