5445,IssuesEvent,2017-04-07 12:34:07+00:00,20022129,podhmo/alchemyjsonschema,795177,nineinchnick,,,opened,Missing support for TSVECTOR,[],[],0,"When generating schema for a model which includes a TSVECTOR column I get the following exception:

```
InvalidStatus: notfound: TSVECTOR. (cls=<class 'sqlalchemy.dialects.postgresql.base.TSVECTOR'>)
```

Such columns are sometimes used instead of a functional index to avoid multiple calls to `to_tsvector()`, for example when planner is filtering results obtained from an index. I'd expect them to be at least ignored in resulting schema.",{},{}
