6277,IssuesEvent,2016-12-04 09:21:53+00:00,75490534,wimglenn/advent-of-code-data,116237,topaz,,,closed,Please don't overload the AoC servers,[],[],5,"*Please* don't make modules like this.  This module requests the user's input every time the script runs; the Advent of Code servers aren't magic and can only handle limited capacity.  Please make your script store the player's input in a file and possibly sleep() before downloading the input to prevent someone calling get_data() in a loop.

