6447,IssuesEvent,2018-01-04 17:14:33+00:00,77217599,SergeyPirogov/webdriver_manager,17965629,usmcamp0811,,,closed,ValueError: There is no such driver phantomjs with version 2.1.2 by https://bitbucket.org/ariya/phantomjs/downloads/phantomjs-2.1.2-windows.zip,[],[],0,"There is a problem getting the PhantonJSDriver. I traced it down to the `driver_tags_url` json @ [https://api.github.com/repos/ariya/phantomjs/tags](https://api.github.com/repos/ariya/phantomjs/tags) having a newer version of the drivers than exist on the download site. 

