So far the only one that works is making one api call for each creative_id, which is not very efficient.
The docs show me that I can make batch api calls. I have tried that, but I must be missing something.

Basically:

```python
get_creatives_one_by_one()  # it works!
get_creatives_using_batch_api()  # it gives me empty objects
```

Below is the complete sample code and corresponding output demonstrating the problem.
Any help is appretiated.

```python
import json
import hmac
