7882,IssuesEvent,2018-07-13 18:54:51+00:00,81979405,upsight/doctor,109865,boralyl,268175,upsight,closed,Add support for typing.Union,[],[],1,"There may be some cases where a parameter can be one of a few types.  The best example would be a parameter that can be a string or a None value.  Example:

