8683,IssuesEvent,2018-06-17 16:33:24+00:00,79510167,pypa/pipenv,954310,techalchemy,647025,pypa,closed,Pipenv should support platform markers in pipenv install and pipenv install -r,[],[],2,"`pipenv install ""nsenter ; platform_system=='Linux'""`
should do the same as `pip install ""...""`, and it should put this in your Pipfile:
