9546,IssuesEvent,2017-02-08 19:44:29+00:00,7444861,zopefoundation/transaction,487237,mmerickel,1163184,zopefoundation,closed,need a simple api to detect an active transaction,[],[],12,"`manager.begin()` will automatically abort an active transaction. The only way to determine if one is active is via `manager._txn is None`. This private api is the only way right now to write a function that starts a new transaction only if one does not already exist. Similarly `manager.get()` will create a transaction if one does not exist.

