11821,IssuesEvent,2017-01-25 16:42:25+00:00,70530854,awslabs/serverless-application-model,43251,jolexa,3299148,awslabs,opened,Changing an Api Event does not redeploy the API resource,[],[],0,"Here is my scenerio:

