12720,IssuesEvent,2016-10-26 06:38:11+00:00,41284151,frictionlessdata/tabulator-py,557395,roll,5912125,frictionlessdata,closed,Merge loader/parser_options to option keywords in stream constructor?,"[{'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/frictionlessdata/tabulator-py/labels/deprecating', 'name': 'deprecating', 'color': 'bfd4f2'}, {'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/frictionlessdata/tabulator-py/labels/feature', 'name': 'feature', 'color': '159818'}, {'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/frictionlessdata/tabulator-py/labels/review', 'name': 'review', 'color': 'fbca04'}]","[{'login': 'roll', 'id': 557395, 'avatar_url': 'https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/557395?v=3', 'gravatar_id': '', 'url': 'https://api.github.com/users/roll', 'html_url': 'https://github.com/roll', 'followers_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/roll/followers', 'following_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/roll/following{/other_user}', 'gists_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/roll/gists{/gist_id}', 'starred_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/roll/starred{/owner}{/repo}', 'subscriptions_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/roll/subscriptions', 'organizations_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/roll/orgs', 'repos_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/roll/repos', 'events_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/roll/events{/privacy}', 'received_events_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/roll/received_events', 'type': 'User', 'site_admin': False}]",0,"# Overview

`tabulator` constructor options is a standard protocol to open a stream for libraries on top it (`jts.Table`, `goodtables` etc). So we need here user-friendly solution.

# Example

Before:
```python
stream = Stream('path.csv', parser_options={'delimeter': ','})
```
After:
```python
stream = Stream('path.csv', delimeter=',')
```

# Tasks
- [x] add to `loaders.Api.supported_options` attribute
- [x] add to `parsers.Api.supported_options` attribute
- [x] add to `writers.Api.supported_options` attribute
- [x] merge `Stream` constructor `loader/parser_options -> **options`
- [x] route passed to `Stream` options based on supported options
- [x] rename `**writer_options` to `**options` in `Stream.save`",{},{}
