13089,IssuesEvent,2015-03-24 15:58:38+00:00,6235174,conda/conda,204215,jrsmith3,6392739,conda,closed,[Question] What data is in the third column of `conda list`,"[{'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/conda/conda/labels/Documentation', 'name': 'Documentation', 'color': 'fbca04'}]",[],3,"I've looked over the documentation and I can't figure out what the third column returned by `conda list` is:

