13136,IssuesEvent,2016-10-19 20:46:19+00:00,6235174,conda/conda,329591,wesm,6392739,conda,closed,Help with RPATH on OS X with cmake,[],[],3,"See the OS X (Travis CI) failure here: https://github.com/conda-forge/staged-recipes/pull/1732

