    openssl-1.0.2o             |                0         3.3 MB  conda-forge
    ca-certificates-2018.4.16  |                0         140 KB  conda-forge
    certifi-2018.4.16          |           py27_0         142 KB  conda-forge
    ------------------------------------------------------------
                                           Total:         4.2 MB

The following packages will be UPDATED:

    ca-certificates: 2018.03.07-0      --> 2018.4.16-0      conda-forge
    certifi:         2018.4.16-py27_0  --> 2018.4.16-py27_0 conda-forge
    conda:           4.5.1-py27_0      --> 4.5.2-py27_0     conda-forge
    openssl:         1.0.2o-h26aff7b_0 --> 1.0.2o-0         conda-forge

Proceed ([y]/n)?
```


## Expected Behavior
<!-- What do you think should happen? -->
`conda` should be updated as the output of `conda` suggests or the message could be more descriptive and report on which channel `conda` is available.

## Environment Information

