13200,IssuesEvent,2015-08-06 19:31:33+00:00,6235174,conda/conda,334496,ilanschnell,6392739,conda,closed,Unable to clone root environment in offline mode,[],[],1,"According to the help pages, it should be possible to create a new environment based off a clone without internet by supplying the --offline and --use-index-cache options. But these don't seem to work, conda insists on retrieving package metadata form the internet.

e.g.
```
PS C:\Users\rfan> conda create rootclone2 --clone root --offline --use-index-cache
Error: either -n NAME or -p PREFIX option required,
       try ""conda create -h"" for more details
PS C:\Users\rfan> conda create -n rootclone2 --clone root --offline --use-index-cache
src_prefix: 'C:\\Program Files\\Anaconda'
dst_prefix: 'C:\\Users\\rfan\\.conda\\envs\\rootclone2'
Packages: 122
Files: 5
Fetching package metadata: Could not connect to https://repo.continuum.io/pkgs/pro/noarch/
Could not connect to https://repo.continuum.io/pkgs/free/win-64/
Could not connect to https://repo.continuum.io/pkgs/free/noarch/
Could not connect to https://repo.continuum.io/pkgs/pro/win-64/
....
An unexpected error has occurred, please consider sending the
following traceback to the conda GitHub issue tracker at:

    https://github.com/conda/conda/issues

Include the output of the command 'conda info' in your report.


Traceback (most recent call last):
  File ""C:\Program Files\Anaconda\Scripts\conda-script.py"", line 4, in <module>
    sys.exit(main())
  File ""C:\Program Files\Anaconda\lib\site-packages\conda\cli\main.py"", line 201, in main
    args_func(args, p)
  File ""C:\Program Files\Anaconda\lib\site-packages\conda\cli\main.py"", line 208, in args_func
    args.func(args, p)
  File ""C:\Program Files\Anaconda\lib\site-packages\conda\cli\common.py"", line 612, in inner
    return func(args, parser)
  File ""C:\Program Files\Anaconda\lib\site-packages\conda\cli\main_create.py"", line 50, in execute
    install.install(args, parser, 'create')
  File ""C:\Program Files\Anaconda\lib\site-packages\conda\cli\install.py"", line 170, in install
    clone(args.clone, prefix, json=args.json, quiet=args.quiet)
  File ""C:\Program Files\Anaconda\lib\site-packages\conda\cli\install.py"", line 91, in clone
    quiet=quiet)
  File ""C:\Program Files\Anaconda\lib\site-packages\conda\misc.py"", line 186, in clone_env
    execute_actions(actions, index=get_index(), verbose=not quiet)
  File ""C:\Program Files\Anaconda\lib\site-packages\conda\plan.py"", line 527, in execute_actions
    inst.execute_instructions(plan, index, verbose)
  File ""C:\Program Files\Anaconda\lib\site-packages\conda\instructions.py"", line 148, in execute_instructions
    cmd(state, arg)
  File ""C:\Program Files\Anaconda\lib\site-packages\conda\instructions.py"", line 52, in FETCH_CMD
    fetch(state['index'], arg)
  File ""C:\Program Files\Anaconda\lib\site-packages\conda\instructions.py"", line 48, in fetch
