### What problem was encountered?
Retry policy did not allow for a retry. HTTP status code=403 blob_service.exists(CONTAINER_NAME)
When this python program is called directly it runs successfully and the file is uploaded into blob in less-than a second. But if it is called from Talend job the Python code fail with this error.
