16867,IssuesEvent,2018-07-20 05:00:28+00:00,55808787,openthread/openthread,16142208,jwhui,16142269,openthread,closed,[nrf52840] device hangs when reinitializing cc310,"[{'id': 355043111, 'node_id': 'MDU6TGFiZWwzNTUwNDMxMTE=', 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/openthread/openthread/labels/bug', 'name': 'bug', 'color': 'ee0701', 'default': True}, {'id': 549834395, 'node_id': 'MDU6TGFiZWw1NDk4MzQzOTU=', 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/openthread/openthread/labels/platform:%20nrf52840', 'name': 'platform: nrf52840', 'color': 'fbca04', 'default': False}]",[],1,"#2878 reinitialize all peripherals except uart for pseudo reset, but it introduced another issue that the device hangs when reinitializing cc310, the issue only exist when OT Dtls related features are enabled (because of #2896).

