18234,IssuesEvent,2017-12-18 01:34:03+00:00,48904888,Cog-Creators/Red-DiscordBot,7438501,Tobotimus,23690422,Cog-Creators,opened,[V3 Streams] Streamalert channels are case sensitive,[],[],0,"### Type:

- [x] Bug

### Brief description of the problem
Two stream alerts can be created for the same channel if they differ in case.

### To reproduce
1. `streamalert twitch channel tobotimus`
2. `streamalert twitch channel TOBOTIMUS`
3. `streamalert twitch channel tobotimus`

Notice how the 2nd step adds a new alert, but the 3rd one removes the 1st.
",{},{}
