18294,IssuesEvent,2018-07-16 06:40:36+00:00,48593532,tensorpack/tensorpack,37792715,zxqcreations,25570510,tensorpack,closed,"Assign requires shapes of both tensors to match. lhs shape= [1,1,4096,4096] rhs shape= [4096,4096]",[],[],4,"Hi,
  I've tried to build my own vgg16 with my code [gennet](https://github.com/zxqcreations/gennet) which is used to generate CNNs. By following vgg's paper, I generated a vgg16 model by myself (use [testgen.py](https://github.com/zxqcreations/gennet/blob/master/testgen.py) to generate a vgg16.ckpt). But when I tried to apply it to `train_faster_rcnn.sh`, I met this issue:

