18772,IssuesEvent,2012-02-20 08:32:32+00:00,3342046,RDFLib/rdflib,16417,gjhiggins,1401847,RDFLib,closed,"lax rdfa parser mode - when html5 parser missing, fall back to the strict one rather than fail",[],[],0,"danbrick...@gmail.com, 2009-12-29T13:49:26.000Z
<pre>
we have lax=True ...

